div.div: In an effort to escape the power struggle within the Heavenly Demon Sect, the protagonist Myeong-Un retreats to a life of seclusion. However, simply avoiding ambition for the throne is not enough to avert tragedy. Myeong-Un flees from the sect leader Myeong-Gak, who seeks fratricide, before meeting his demise. At the moment of his death, as his consciousness fades, he hears a voice. "Do you regret it? Do you wish to fight again?"" To his surprise, Myeong-Un, believed to be dead, opens his eyes once more.... (Source: WEBTOONS)
Wo De Zong Men Yi Dian Qiang

Wang Feng finds himself transmigrated to the Xian Lan Continent. With the help of the powerful Zongmen System, he can summon all sorts of powerful minions to crush all opposition, leading his sect of immortals to unparalleled glory.

(Source: iQIYI, translated)
